<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Married At First Sight star Lizzie Sobinoff is more loved-up than ever with her boyfriend, Seb Guilhaus.</p>

<p>And on Sunday, the 29-year-old exchanged engraved silver thumb rings with the hunky personal trainer. </p>

